{"tid":818219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【理科撚機會黎啦】香港天文台招聘科學主任，截止申請日期：2018年9月28日","createTime":"2018-09-14T03:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:56:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad5588164b57b6bbe27d1819f7341afb9a04a52","tid":818219,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.weather.gov.hk/whatsnew/r2/whatsnew_20180907_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.gov.hk%2Fwhatsnew%2Fr2%2Fwhatsnew_20180907_uc.htm&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=7bf361f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weather.gov.hk/whatsnew/r2/whatsnew_20180907_uc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n新一輪的科學主任*招聘已開始（2018年9月7日）。今次由身兼天氣節目主持人Eunice (科學主任李鳳瑩小姐) 為大家介紹天文台科學主任的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DAvVcW6uMe4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDAvVcW6uMe4&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=09b1a7ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DAvVcW6uMe4</a><br />\n<br />\n科學主任的工作充份利用科學、創新及多元合作以服務社會，並且擁抱國際視野，是一份極具挑戰及有意義的工作。<br />\n<br />\n要了解天文台多元化的工作與挑戰，請瀏覽天文台「事業＠香港天文台」網頁。今期科學主任招聘的截止申請日期為2018年9月28日，不要錯過加入我們大家庭的機會啊！<br />\n<br />\n*科學主任主要負責執行天氣預測職務，督導及訓練員工，以及研究和提供包括天氣、氣候、地震、輻射、水文氣象、海洋物理、航空氣象、海洋氣象和應用氣象等服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee1421c44f38ef16bc9812d353a582d37e711df","tid":818219,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"原來要返shift<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5f46cc80daab5ff86f5a71152ea23b83f3a806","tid":818219,"uid":95,"like":4,